Paul Scherrer (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Scherrer_(actor) 0 Paul Gallagher Scherrer (born December 16, 1968) is a realtor and former American stage, film and television actor. He began his career as a child actor on the stage. Scherrer retired from acting in 2001 and now lives and works in Indianapolis.
